{"tid":406882,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《環時》斥香港大學生借上莊「泡妞」","createTime":"2017-09-20T04:19:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-20T05:38:41.000Z","uid":5195,"like":6,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"adf3781f0682bc314201d570672a979c0d69e627","tid":406882,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T04:19:16.000Z","msg":"香港多間大學近日出現「港獨」標語，內地《環球時報》今（20日）發表報道，指本港大學的學生會是「港獨溫床」，先藉此結識港獨份子，大學畢業後再從政散播港獨。<br />\n報道又引述，前香港教育工作者聯會主席兼將軍澳香島中學校長鄧飛接受訪問時指，學生會是獨立於大學之外的社會團體，並不隸屬於大學。大學生上莊只有兩大理由，分別是「政治演練」和「泡妞」。"},{"pid":"d94fa8d8948ea8cf2dfec5bb27ad00e51c787a8d","tid":406882,"uid":75692,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T04:19:53.000Z","msg":"on撚9 而家先知?"},{"pid":"4088e141b1386ebd97b267431e7adbaa94e9aa44","tid":406882,"uid":90601,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T04:20:30.000Z","msg":"溝囡有錯？"},{"pid":"8fed7c0ca3678043b6814f5377278e8f5a3f3ec1","tid":406882,"uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T04:20:31.000Z","msg":"So?"},{"pid":"0d54c4974b09737de99b8b37824991d17a1fae0f","tid":406882,"uid":38671,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T04:21:34.000Z","msg":"小學雞咩<br />\n講粗口又唔得，溝女又唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d768a3fdd11102b1c63f30acf9c14836099ae29d","tid":406882,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T04:23:05.000Z","msg":"係又點?<br />\n<br />\nON<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12421211ab83953430e948426f27cec292a9b01e","tid":406882,"uid":14449,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T04:23:39.000Z","msg":"唔溝女/仔就唔撚正常啦"},{"pid":"58d9f5d93f47c54c85ee1dc000956e606f64d28d","tid":406882,"uid":46197,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T04:23:46.000Z","msg":"讀大學唔溝女，有乜做"},{"pid":"8656f8911f5a24c7a7234f458470b95bc798a5e0","tid":406882,"uid":136431,"li